Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 06:55:57 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] feat(v3): colorful footer column titles + rainbow skills
 + tailwind safelist

- Footer column titles are now colored:
  EXPLORE (emerald), RESOURCES (purple), LEGAL (amber), SOCIAL (cyan)
- Portfolio Skills section: each group card gets its own accent color
  (Frontend=emerald, Backend=purple, Databases=amber, Programming=cyan,
  DevTools=pink, AI=blue, Web3=emerald). Section number badges match.
  Skill pills use badge-{color} tinted style instead of monochrome.
- tailwind.config.js safelist: prevents purge of dynamic icon-{color},
  badge-{color}, text-brand-{color} classes. Fixes 5th free-tool tile
  (Email Header Analyzer) that was previously rendering without its
  gradient icon container.
---
 app/portfolio/page.js | 14 +++++++++-----
 components/Footer.jsx |  8 ++++----
 tailwind.config.js    |  6 ++++++
 3 files changed, 19 insertions(+), 9 deletions(-)

